sequenceDiagram
    actor Investor
    participant System as Auto Investment<br/>Notifier System
    participant DB as Alert Database
    participant StockAPI as Stock API

    Investor->>System: Manage Stock Alerts
    System->>DB: Get tracked stocks & alerts
    DB-->>System: Stock & alert list
    System-->>Investor: Display alert list

    Investor->>System: Create / Update Alert
    System->>Investor: Request alert details
    Investor->>System: Enter threshold & condition

    System->>System: Validate alert rules

    alt Valid alert details
        System->>DB: Save / update alert
        DB-->>System: Save successful
        System-->>Investor: Alert saved successfully
    else Invalid threshold or rule
        System-->>Investor: Error message (invalid rule)
    end

    opt Stock identifier check
        System->>StockAPI: Validate stock symbol
        StockAPI-->>System: Symbol valid / invalid
    end

    Investor->>System: View updated alert list
    System->>DB: Fetch updated alerts
    DB-->>System: Updated alert list
    System-->>Investor: Show updated alerts